{"tid":2304214,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"人事音書●從法無所禁到無所不禁 - 余家強","createTime":"2020-11-28T14:29:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T14:29:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"76ca7ca5f16dda112203ab10fdf24210d2e26dfa","tid":2304214,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T14:29:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201128/RWFRW7VWTNFYPFL4O37UZDXUV4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201128%2FRWFRW7VWTNFYPFL4O37UZDXUV4%2F&d=7TTtdOR49HUCBqTToLMoR3GrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=bb6967df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201128%2FRWFRW7VWTNFYPFL4O37UZDXUV4%2F&h=6e70ede2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201128/RWFRW7VWTNFYPFL4O37UZDXUV4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n人事音書●從法無所禁到無所不禁 - 余家強<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/lYSvvG5eMo6EohkPMs_U_U4wNNQ=/891x707/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PX6F4JA5IVGJRF3IBMU4WUDN4Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FlYSvvG5eMo6EohkPMs_U_U4wNNQ%3D%2F891x707%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPX6F4JA5IVGJRF3IBMU4WUDN4Q.jpg&h=365ae877&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n與朋友路經商場，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n言之有理，但想深一層。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n若一早寄望場所東主及。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n當權者負責任把條例。。。<br />\n<br />\n中華傳統卻非。。。<br />\n<br />\n傳統觀念還偉大，引申發展到現代中國仲得人驚：朕白紙黑字寫清楚的，你固然得遵守；朕沒寫清楚的，你也得遵守！因為你要醒目識do、自閹、自我檢查。國安法下，港府發聲明指光時八字涉違反規定，ok姑且忍受，轉頭葛珮帆跳出來說以「康復香港 時代抗疫」為口號的口罩廠「充滿暗示性」、「打擦邊球」，同樣喊取締，翌日Yellow Factory門市應聲停業，便完全龍門任由佢搬了。<br />\n<br />\n朋友，法律不能禁止埋擦邊球的，若然，許多幽默感不知從何談起，大家動輒得咎，倒不如乾脆變啞巴？別的不說，單單謝偉俊「光復積金 錢袋革命」也請一視同仁予以譴責吧。<br />\n<br />\n自相矛盾，標準把尺只在當權者心中，因為你要識do，法無所禁，卻有更高層次無所不禁。<br />\n<br />\n「犯法呀？差人拉呀？」以前黃子華《棟篤笑》常常講的台詞，骨子裏也是法無所禁即凡事放心率性而為，今後還能夠玩此幽默嗎？你無犯法，不過，差人照拉你。"}]}